      "text": "ほら、琴乃。今日は琴乃の服を買いに来たんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ Kotono. We’re here to buy clothes for you today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9999997933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あれを試着したいとか、どんどん言ってくれないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve gotta tell me what you want to try on‚ one after another.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7847062685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
