      "text": "なんでお姉ちゃんが、そんな気合い入れてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you so fired up about this‚ sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2666661421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.0669610817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-14.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、琴乃をもっと可愛くしたいからね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ because I want to make you even cuter!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0669610817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
