    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_think-05.m4a",
      "text": "それに琴乃の服って、私のお下がりばっかりでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And most of your clothes are my hand-me-downs‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5669599373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自分で自分の着たい服を選びたくない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t you want to choose what you want to wear yourself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.766962115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6002944151
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私はお姉ちゃんと違って、服とかよく分からないし\nお下がりでも、そんな気にしてないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not like you—I don’t really know much about clothes.\nAnd I don’t really mind wearing hand-me-downs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.2428790886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
