      "text": "ダ～メ！　それは私に似合うかなって選んだ服だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nooope! Those are clothes I picked because I thought they’d suit me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2428790886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "琴乃には琴乃だけの、似合う服がきっとあるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are definitely clothes out there that suit you—and only you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2923466972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
